        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">DEIFIED (12pts) and RACECAR (11pts) are 7-letter palindromes — <span class="text-white font-medium">they qualify for the bingo bonus</span>. A DEIFIED bingo scores 62 points. A RACECAR bingo scores 61 points. Rare but spectacular.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
